content.html: Log4j 2.16.0 has already announced this morning and I have just completed my 6am to 4am shift!😵‍💫World is on fire 🔥, yet it was a pleasure to do something with all Log4j developers: @rgoers @RemkoPopma @carter_kozak @jvz @GaryGregory, Ron Grabowski, Robert Middleton. 🍩
